(26, 130, 'Simha', 'leo', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Leo is called Simha Rashi in Vedic Astrology. &nbsp;The naturally fiery sign rules the east direction and is a male by gender. It gives Pitta Dosha. It controls the stomach, spinal cord and back. <a title="surya article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Surya</a> is the lord of Simha Rashi.</p>\r\n<h4>Chandra in Simha Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Simha Rashi is another name for royalty. Whether the native is rich or poor one thing is guaranteed that he would live a king-sized life. Simha natives are fond of flair and pomp. They have abundance of pride and self-esteem. At the same time they are kind, honest, happy and forgiving type. Simha natives are blessed with all the attributes of Surya like good will power, ambition and foresight. At the same time they are also blessed with arrogance, aggression and egoism. Simha natives generally rise through their own efforts. They are incredibly hard working and determined to succeed in any area they plunge into.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;One peculiar feature of Simha natives is the large and prominent eyes. Also they have huge forehead and well formed teeth. Their physical build is thin and strong. They speak in a loud, clear and concise manner. They are full of vigor and vitality and do not get tired easily. They like to show off and often arrange parties and celebrations. They would be the first ones to beat drums about their achievements and success. Even a role as Social Activist is more likely to be to show off albeit to promote social causes. Simha natives have fondness for clothes and fashion and like to wear clothes which make them look like royalty. Simha natives like open houses which allows abundant air and sunlight to enter. If they are rich they often opt for Palaces and Castles which allow open air to flow as well allows to show off their riches. The greatest asset of Simha natives is their abundant will power which makes them successful in anything they set out to do.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;The downside of abundant willpower is the inability to comprehend failures and limitations of others. At business and workplace they are a nightmare to work with. While the employers maybe very happy due to their nature of overexertion but fellow employees and employees working below are certainly not. Simha natives are ideally suited for management roles. They are not the type to venture into a business by creating a debt. Career in Teaching, Stock Markets, Management, Chemical Engineering, Pharmacy and even as an Entrepreneur gives good results. Other professions include Government Jobs, Working as a Trustee, Accountancy and Agriculture. The best career for Simha natives is as a Politician or Entertainment Business where there is abundant limelight on them.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Simha natives do not get on too well with siblings, family members and friends. Generally they are dominant personality among the family members. They have few friends due to their arrogant and aggressive attitude. In marriage and romance they tend to excel as long as the partner is a passive personality. They are quite romantic by nature and very likely to opt for love marriage. As long as partner is happy playing the second fiddle and let the Simha native take centerstage there are no problems indicated in marriage. But if the partner has similar personality then all hell breaks loose. Other point is the placement of Kumbha Rashi in <a title="7th house article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=16:kalatra-bhava&amp;catid=11:12-bhavas&amp;Itemid=119">7th house</a> from Simha native. <a title="kumbha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=32:aquarius&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Kumbha Rashi</a> is the rashi of <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shani</a> and Shani is the karka for dissolution and divorces. Hence forewarned for Simha natives is to be careful in marriage and not to let small arguments and ego issues ruin their marriage.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Arrogance, Anger, Sarcasm, Hogging Limelight</p>\r\n<p>Diseases: Generally they are quite healthy. Although Heart Problems, Acidity, Acne, Eye Diseases and Problems in lower back are possible. Piles are common if other fiery planets are associated with Chandra in Simha Rashi.</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:27:43', 899, '', '2014-04-29 07:14:39', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:27:43', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 16, 6, 'simha, leo, rashi ruled by surya, simha rashi marriage, simha rashi career', 'simha rashi in vedic astrology', 1, 70, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(27, 132, 'Kanya', 'virgo', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Virgo is known as Kanya Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is an earthy sign, female by gender and rules the south direction. It give both Vata Dosha and Kapha Dosha. Budh is the lord of Kanya Rashi. <a title="budh article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:budh&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Budh</a> is exalted and <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a> is debilitated in Kanya Rashi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Chandra in Kanya Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Chandra in kanya rashi is in its enemy rashi. Kanya is ruled by Budh who doesn''t see eye to eye which Chandra. Any association of Chandra+Budh gives some sort of mental disease, mental disorder or weak mind and nervous system. Generally the mind is weak and too many thoughts often cloud judgement of Kanya natives. Ofcourse the picture is not all that black. Kanya natives (Chandra in Kanya rashi) are trustworthy, obedient and have excellent character and personality They are blessed with an above average IQ and can remember events for a very long time. Also they have excellent business sense.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Kanya natives have slanty eyes and prominent forehead. They have a raddish complexion and long nose. They have a faint smile and attractive lips. Like Budh they remain younger and attractive and age doesn''t catch up with them. They attract a lot of friends due to their good character and personality. They need to take care not to lose confidence when undertaking a task. Though life may give many ups and downs they get abundant opportunities to progress. Kanya natives are advised to forge a fortune through hard work and concrete efforts as chances of getting lucky are few and far. They can try to settle abroad and can be quite fortunate on foreign shores. Kanya natives have many qualities of ruler Budh like laziness, talkative, calculative in finances and certain amount of princely attitude. There are many good traits in Kanya natives like love for animals and research minded attitude.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Kanya natives generally prefer to do business as opposed to doing job at an workplace. With their nature of economical spending they generally do not suffer from finance issues when starting a business. They are excellent negotiators and ideal career is suggested as Counselor, Negotiator, Diplomat or Peace Broker. They can eventually gather a great amount of fortune. Kanya natives know their limitations and do not work beyond them which actually works in their favor. Still career is full of ups and downs due to Chandra-Budh relationship and prayers to Lord Vishnu and Lord Shiva are advised. Kanya natives can pursue a wide range of professions including Journalism, Medicine, Law, Teaching, Accountancy and Astrology.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Kanya natives generally settle for arranged marriage and chances of romance maybe less compared to other rashis. Many a times late marriage is observed. Kanya natives are faithful and compassionate in their marriage. They practice discipline and prefer monogamy in life. They are unable to forgive partners even for some small fault, lie or deceit. Kanya natives need to learn the art of forgiving and forgetting in order to enjoy a good marital life. Also they need to take care their emotions do not get the better of them in a married life.</p>\r\n<p>Diseases include pain in lower back. Mental diseases possible due to Chandra+Budh relationship. This can lead to other diseases like indigestion, flatulence, acidity and weak constitution. Muscle cramps and ulcers are observed in old age.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Mental Anxiety, Stingy, Dual Personality.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:30:47', 899, '', '2014-04-29 11:15:14', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:30:47', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 15, 5, 'kanya, virgo, rashi ruled by budh, kanya rashi career, kanya rashi health, kanya rashi diseases', 'kanya rashi in vedic astrology', 1, 139, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(28, 134, 'Tula', 'libra', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; Libra is known as Tula Rashi in Vedic Astrology. The windy sign rules the west direction and is a male by gender. It controls the kidneys and urinary system as well as sexual organs. It gives Vatta Dosha. <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a> is the lord of Tula Rashi. <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shani</a> is exalted and <a title="surya article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Surya</a> is debilitated in Tula Rashi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Tula Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Tula Rashi suggests a native who are balance in their views. Tula natives are happy go lucky, intelligent, kind and calm-minded. Along with it the Shukra based qualities like fashionista attitude, fond of sweets and delicacies, addicted to forbidden pleasures of life are also observed in Tula natives. They have an aristrocatic way of talking and prefer good lifestyle. All negatives cannot make up for the one positive of providing balance view and judgement without any sort of malice or envy when asked to give an opinion. They are the ideal people to go to when there is a need for free and fair judgement to be given.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Tula natives have small eyes and attractive lips and nose. They are light brownish or whitish in color. They have long and beautiful hair (both male and females). They speak in a slow and sweet manner. Often saliva comes out when they speak. Tula natives are well behaved and approach everyone with kindness. While they are balanced in giving judgements they themselves often lose balance due to Shukra traits endowed in them. Sometimes they talk too little while other times they become too chatty. They are very much into pleasures, addictions and sex and that destroys their balance in life. They have a good education but generally go into another profession as compared to their field of study. They may not be that benevolent but they are also considerate enough so as to not cause harm to others. They are fond of music, food and travel. They look younger then their age. Generally tula natives have no control over finances and believe in over-spending. Tula natives stay cheerful and do not like to get angry at people. Tula natives make a habit of putting their point across. They are clean, tidy and hygienic.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Tula natives have excellent career credentials and can be successful in many fields. They can do excellent in law as lawyer or judge. Other industries include Beauty Products, Fashion Industry, Entertainment Industry, Acting and Photography. They can also be successful in Oil Import-Export and also business related to Water maybe beneficial. They can even make a good Politician. Most of the successful Politicians have Tula Lagna.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;In family matters tula natives tend to derive more love from their father as compared to the mother. They get along well with siblings. They try to be father figure (both male and females) for their children. In romance and marriage they tend to have multiple relationships before marriage. Marriage generally is love marriage but even if arranged marriage takes place, native likely to keep decision of choosing partner on himself/herself. 7th house rules marriage and 7th house for Tula Rashi is <a title="mesha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:aries&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Mesha Rashi</a>. Naturally the partner (signified by <a title="7th house article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=16:kalatra-bhava&amp;catid=11:12-bhavas&amp;Itemid=119">7th house</a>) is fiery and hot tempered. So in either case Tula natives have to accept the passive personality in marriage to sustain their marriage.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Overspending, Fixed Views, Prone to Addictions</p>\r\n<p>Diseases: Diseases of Kidney, Urinal Tract, Sexual Organs and Intestine are all possible for Tula natives. Kidney Stones, Urinal Tract Infection, Pain in Intestine, Liver Problems, Cough and Cold are all possible. Constipacy and other common digestive problems related to intestine are possible.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:34:24', 899, '', '2014-05-01 07:33:15', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:34:24', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 15, 4, 'tula rashi, libra sign, rashi ruled by shukra, tula rashi health, tula rashi diseases, tula rashi marriage, tula rashi career', 'tula rashi in vedic astrology', 1, 92, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(29, 136, 'Vrischika', 'scorpio', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Scorpio is known as Vrischika Rashi in Vedic Astrology. This watery sign is a female by gender and rules over the north direction. It controls the uterus, bladder and excretary system. <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a> is the lord of Vrischika Rashi while <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> is debilitated in Vrischika Rashi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Chandra in Vrischika Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Chandra in Vrischika is in its neecha rashi. Vrischika natives are often mentally weak and panic unnecessarily. But they are hard working, extremely clever and blessed with a sharp memory which is able to accurately remember minute information. As long as someone doesn''t hurt their feelings they behave in a friendly, helpful and compassionate manner. If their feelings are hurt they are prone to resort to vengeance to get even and behave in a spiteful manner. No matter what the inner scenario in the head the outward physical appearance of Vrischika natives is calm and composed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Vrischika natives have big eyes, pointed nose and long neck. They often have wrinkles on forehead. A peculiar trait is their ability to talk continuously without ever understanding a given subject of discussion. They have very hard time explaining their point across to others. There have dull facial expressions which makes it difficult for them to get the point across. If this small flaw is overlooked they are great people to be with who are ever ready and willing to help others without any sort of expectation in return. Vrischika natives are not the type to cause harm to others for personal benefit. They might even let go of profit for others to avoid harm. There are exceptions involved when <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shani</a> or Mangal are associated which makes Vrischika natives think of personal benefit first but in normal scenario when no malefic association is present Vrischika natives are kind and considerate to others. Vrischika natives are creative, focused and can put considerable efforts into task at hand. While they have a weak mind it generally doesn''t affect their ability to do hard work. The symbol for Vrischika Rashi is a Scorpion and like a Scorpion it gets on with work until harassed or if someone gets in its way. Once someone makes enemies with Vrischika natives they are the type to take revenge on enemies with full vengeance and spite. Vrischika natives are warned to learn the art of forgiving and forgetting to progress. Also prayers to Lord Shiva are highly beneficial. Another downside of Vrischika natives is their inability to change inspite of points which may drag them down.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Career for Vrischika natives may have some ups and downs. Chandra in Mangal rashi is a sure shot career in medicine and chemicals. A great career as a doctor, pharmacist, chemist, engineering, chemical processing and electrics is possible. Also career in Criminal Investigation, Army, Detective Agency, Insurance and Banking Sector is also possible. Vrischika natives are not known to have too much fame and fortune owing to their righteous and helpful nature. Also they have hard time to get their point across which makes it difficult to sell their products. Generally advised to do role in Service Sector. Although Business may favor them if other positive factors are present in horoscope.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Family for Vrischika natives is a mixed baggage. They generally do not derive much help from parents and make their career through their own efforts. Relationship with siblings is either bad or somewhat decent. Generally no help is derived from siblings but harm and legal troubles have been seen with siblings. In matters of marriage the partner be it male or female is the better half. 7th from Vrischika Rashi is <a title="vrisabha article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:taurus&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Vrisabha Rashi</a> which shows a beautiful, well-cultured and good partner. There maybe issues with partner due to anger, difference of opinions and suspect attitute towards partners morality. Vrischika natives are advised to avoid unnecessary suspect on spouse as well as avoid petty arguments and fights. Vrischika natives are very caring for their children but as the children grow up there are bound to be difference of opinion with the children especially sons. It is best to let children take their own independent decisions in life once they grow up.</p>\r\n<p>Diseases: Generally health is very goood. There are problems associated with small intestine and sexual organs. Also urinal tract, bladder and vagina maybe prone to ailments. Area around these parts is also ruled by Vrischika Rashi and care needs to be taken with diseases related to these parts. Other common diseases include cold and pain in neck. Vrischika natives are prone to accidents and injuries.</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Revengeful, Indecisive, Unwilling to Change, Charitable at Cost of Personal Health &amp; Finances.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:36:13', 899, '', '2014-05-01 07:30:39', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:36:13', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 16, 3, 'vrischika rashi, scorpio sign, rashi ruled by mangal, vrischika rashi health, vrischika rashi diseases, vrischika rashi career', 'vrischika rashi in vedic astrology', 1, 72, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(30, 138, 'Dhana', 'sagittarius', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Saggitarius is popularly known as Dhana Rashi (not to be confused with <a title="2nd house article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=11:dhana-bhava&amp;catid=11:12-bhavas&amp;Itemid=119">dhana bhava</a>) in Vedic Astrology. Dhana Rashi is a fiery sign, by gender a male and rules the east direction. It causes Pitta Dosha. It controls the thighs. <a title="guru article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Guru</a> is the lord of Dhana Rashi and <a title="rahu article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Rahu</a> is said to be neecha in Dhana Rashi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Chandra in Dhana Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Dhana Rashi is in the rashi of its friend Guru. Dhana natives are kind, independent, simple and trustworthy. They have firm faith in religion and God. They are endowed with all the good and bad qualities of Guru but the qualities of Chandra are somewhat washed away due to Dhana being a fiery sign who doesn''t bond well with watery Chandra. They are somewhat lazy and prone to anger.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Dhana natives are medium in height with a muscular and sturdy body, long face and big ears. They have slanty eyes and speech is direct. They are happy and fortunate and own a good number of friends. They are blessed in matters of vehicle, property and mother. Dhana natives prefer an independent lifestyle free of interference. Ofcourse it normally doesn''t happen leading to frustration and anger in Dhana natives life. They are straight talking and fearless in approach. Compared to <a title="meena rashi article" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=33:pisces&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Meena Rashi</a> which is also ruled by Guru, Dhana natives have less fame and fortune. But they make up for it through good health and more dominant personality. They can easily subdue their enemies when the need arises. Dhana Rashi is a fiery sign which leads to evaporation of Chandra qualities like emotions, calm and compassion for others. Inside they might be kind and considerate but Dhana natives are unable to show those feelings on the outside. Dhana natives speak their mind out without thinking of consequences and often the speech is rough. Guru as lord of lagna or Chandra Rashi is unlikely to cause harm to others and Dhana natives similarly don''t harm others for their own wellbeing. They may get angry at others but quite unlikely to hold a grudge over a long period of time. Their biggest drawback is their dual standards for themselves and others. In their own life they prefer no interference but when it comes to others they are the first ones to give unwanted advice or taunt others.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;In career matters any profession associated with speech is ideal to pursue. Career in teaching, managment, administration, as a doctor, business tycoon, personality development, religious priest, spiritual guru and even journalism can fetch good income. Any profession associated with Guru is also ideal to pursue. Dhana natives can pursue business but they are advised to avoid partnership in business. Also to keep away from Stock Markets and Gambling.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;For Dhana natives family relationship are complicated due to their nature. They don''t like interference in personal life but can''t resist speaking their mind in others matter. Naturally relationship sour due to it with family members. Inspite of it they have a very kind and loving mother who cares for their well being. They have better equation with friends as compared to family members. They have a good amount of friends and well wishers. In a marriage personal space and privacy is required for marriage to endure. Many a times Dhana natives prefer individual freedom in relationship but can''t give that to the partner. Some rules and regulations are advised to be followed in a marriage. Also dhana natives are advised to appreciate the partner, not insult the partner in public places and social functions. Relationship with children is mostly sour. Dhana natives are best advised not to be too harsh to children. Also avoid unnecessary advise to children.</p>\r\n<p>Diseases may include cough, cold, typhoid, stomach and shoulder pain. Also possible are pain, cramps and injuries in calf muscles. Dhana natives are generally blessed with good health and long life.</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Anger, Arrogance, Hypocrisy, Not Emotional.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:43:34', 899, '', '2014-05-01 09:57:29', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:43:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 21, 1, 'dhana rashi, saggitarius sign, rashi ruled by guru, dhana rashi health, dhana rashi diseases, dhana rashi career', 'dhana rashi in vedic astrology', 1, 58, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(31, 140, 'Makara', 'capricorn', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Capricorn is popularly known as Makara in Vedic Astrology. This earthy sign is female by gender and rules the south direction. It gives both Vatta and Pitta Dosha. It controls both the knee joints and parts around it. <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shani</a> is the lord of Makara Rashi. <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a> is exalted and <a title="guru article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Guru</a> is debilitated in makara.</p>\r\n<h4>Chandra in Makara Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Chandra in Makara Rashi is in the rashi of its enemy Shani. Shani and Chandra are polar opposites in persoanlity. Hence Chandra is not too much comfortable in the rashi of Shani where it has to observe rules and regulations. But where there are rules and regulations, there is success to be followed. So it is not a bad thing to have this precarious position for Chandra. Makara natives are quite ambitious in life. There are handicaps like unnecessary worry and mental diseases.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Makara natives have long neck and short or medium stature. Hair maybe less on head and baldness possible with age. Face is round while eyes are small. A lot of body hair is observed. Due to thin body the veins on the body are visible especially on hands. Makara natives are serious and disciplined in life. They are careful in thoughts, speech and action.They have a rigid nature and generally do not open up to strangers. They have an introvert personality. Other traits include being just, firm once they pick views and stingy in spending. They have a lot of negativity in thoughts and generally see the half empty glass in life. For the enemies Makara natives are quite full of hatred and vengeance. They have few friends and well wishers due to their introvert personality. They are unable to truly open up to others or trust them implicitly. Many a times their own mind and thoughts become a prison for them and that stalls progress. Often the mind experiences depression, anger, anxiety, doubt, envy, panic and other negative emotions. Makara natives often see delay, obstruction and unforeseen circumstances in their life. Care is required not to be bogged down during those tough times.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;In career Makara natives are often confused which career path would be beneficial. There are enough hardships, delays, physical and mental ailments to deal with and progress comes late. But once they pass through their test they become very ambitious and willing to work their way to the top. In a way all the difficulties inject them a sense of hope, ambition and sincerity to achieve success in life. Ultimately they do make a success out of themselves. Makara natives are highly advised to pursue business after certain period of life has passed. Career in garments, government jobs, as builder and color chemical is possible. They can be successful in any business associated with Shani like Oil Import-Export, Iron and Iron Ore, Steel, Running a Website and Accountancy among others.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;In family matters native doesn''t get well with friends or family. His secretive personality, doubting nature and negative emotions make him a kill joy. Normally Makara natives do not get much love and affection from mother but father may provide appropriate care, attention and help in career of native. Still it is doubtful if father maybe able to understand the native due to the natives secretive personality. Friends are few and quite a few times back-stab the Makara natives. It is advised for Makara natives to keep information confidential from friends and well-wishers. Makara native get well along with elders in the household especially grand mother and grand father. Average relationship is observed with the children. Native begets a great partner as 7th house from Makara Rashi is ruled by Karka Rashi. Partner is beautiful, understanding, kind and in ever way the better half of native. Though late marriage is a very likely scenario.</p>\r\n<p>Diseases of the mind like depression, anxiety and schizophrenia are all possible. Also troubles in Knee Joints is possible. At old age knee-joint replacement surgery maybe necessary. Other diseases include indigestion due to excessive thinking, problems of kidney, diabetes, pain in urinal tract. Sometimes paralysis is also possible. &nbsp;Generally bad health has been observed for Makara natives.</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Introvert, Mentall Weak, Overtly Ambitious, Unforgiving Nature, Negative Thoughts.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:44:07', 899, '', '2014-05-01 12:19:53', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:44:07', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 9, 2, 'makara rashi, capricorn sign, rashi ruled by shani', 'makara rashi in vedic astrology', 1, 51, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(32, 142, 'Kumbha', 'aquarius', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Aquarius is known as Kumbha in Vedic Astrology. This windy sign has a male gender and rules the west direction . It gives Vayu Dosha. It rules the feet especially the parts below knee joints. <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shani</a> is the lord of Kumbha rashi while <a title="rahu article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Rahu</a> is said to be exalted in Kumbha.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Chandra in Kumbha Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Kumbha rashi is in the rashi of its enemy Shani. Kumbha natives are very hard to judge cause of their discreet nature. They are generally serious and show restraint in speech and emotions. That is why it is hard to decipher there true intentions. Kumbha natives when passing through difficulties show a tensed look. Kumbha natives are blessed with good analyzing ability and look at all the pros and cons of a situation before taking final judgment. They have good foresight and sometimes have been observed to have sixth sense.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Kumbha natives are short or medium in height. Eyes are small and looks are decent. They are generally thin and possess a long face. Chandra with any association to Shani causes doubts and anxiety in the native. Kumbha natives cannot look beyond the negative side of things and overanalyze a situation. Thus they put brakes on a task even before any work on it has started. Many times great ideas and thoughts never see the light of day for Kumbha natives. They are advised to pursue a task if it is worthy and discard profit-loss and success-failures associated with the task. There is panic and anxiety clearly visible on their faces when under stress or under difficult circumstances. They often turn depressive due to overthinking and worrying too much. Kumbha natives are passive and calm and dislike flashy people who have a habit of showoff. Kumbha natives also possess a great amount of envy for people who are more successful then them. Kumbha natives are duty bound and honest and can provide sound advise without ever forcing their views on others. Kumbha natives have hard time focusing on any given task for long periods of time. Kumbha natives are very sensitive and do not take insults lightly. They are not the type to insult anyone or malign anyone unless malefics like Shani and <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a> are associated with Chandra in Kumbha Rashi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Career for Kumbha natives is excellent where analysis and observation are required. Ideal career as a researcher or scientist. Besides that other career options include social work, software analysis, geography, electronics and even aviation sector. Ideally a career in job sector is better but depending on other factors in horoscope a career in business is also possible. Kumbha natives don''t get along well with employers and remain strict towards employees working under them. Kumbha natives are better to avoid Stock Markets and Gambling.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;In family matters Kumbha natives beget a kind and loving mother who is clever and looks after natives likes and dislikes. Children maybe few and come after considerable effort. Equation with father is either so-so or bad depending on other factors. Rivalry and fights with siblings possible. Not may friends at same time have been observed for Kumbha natives and most of them are untrustworthy. Kumbha natives often change the company of friends they keep. Marriage is late and often after many rejections of opposite candidates by Kumbha natives. Many a times they keep their false hopes on object of attraction or first crush. Marriage is delayed and possibilities or possibilities of frictions in marriage if early.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Diseases: Due to tension and anxiety comon problems like cough, cold, indigestion and stomach pain are likely. Also diseases in urinal tract are possible. Diabetes and problems in blood circulation also likely. Pain, Cramps and Accidents of thigh region rise if Chandra in Kumbha Rashi is aspected or associated by malefics.</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Overthinking, Tensed, Unable To Act On Ideas, Unable To Focus.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:45:20', 899, '', '2014-05-08 07:24:32', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:45:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 22, 1, 'kumbha rashi, aquarius sign, rashi ruled by shani, kumbha rashi health, kumbha rashi diseases, kumbha rashi career', 'kumbha rashi in vedic astrology', 1, 77, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(33, 144, 'Meena', 'pisces', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Pisces is known as Meena Rashi in Vedic Astrology. It is a watery sign, female by gender and rules the north direction. It gives Kapha Dosha. It rules the foot and heels. <a title="guru article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Guru</a> is the lord of Meena Rashi. <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a> is exalted and <a title="budh article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:budh&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Budh</a> is debilitated in Meena Rashi.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>Chandra in Meena Rashi</h4>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Meena is in the rashi of its friend Guru. Meena natives inherit qualities of both the calm Guru and caring Chandra. Apart from bad health, Chandra in Meena is ideal in every other way. Meena natives are well cultured, kind, happy and loving. Guru is an expansive graha and Chandra in Guru''s rashi provides an over-expansive imagination, feelings and emotions Meena natives have an excellent grasping power and have a way with words. They are simple yet attractive due to their lovable personality. They are kind, affectionate, thoughtful and can give sound advise when the need arises.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Meena natives have round or oval face with slanty eyes. Height is medium and body is healthy and even obese in some case. They have a passive yet effective speech while ear slobs are glued to back of head. Meena natives may have good amount of land property but they keep it very untidy. One of the best traits of Meena natives is ability to stay calm and composed even when abuses are hurled at them. Generally fortune smile late after 33-36 years of life. They can even get good inheritance through parental property. While Meena natives are passive and calm most of the times, Chandra traits can make them resort to emotional outburst when they are emotionally hurt. But Meena natives are not likely to keep anger and hatred for long. Meena natives beget the bad qualities of Guru and Chandra like emotional nature, gluttony, obese body, laziness, procrastination and inability to prioritize. Other then few drawbacks Meena natives are kind, impartial and largehearted. They would help anyone who need help irrelevant of status, relation or personal benefit.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Career for Meena natives can extend to wide range of fields. They can do wonders in public dealing and diplomatic relationship. They are blessed with a great imagination and can be good fictional writers. They can do import-export business via ocean/river route which would provide good benefits. Other career fields include doctor, medicine, criminal biology, chemical experts and consulting physician. Besides career as trustee, singer and teaching is also possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Meena natives get on well with friends and family members. They have a loving mother and a very supportive father. Relation with sibling is on good terms most of the time. Spouse is clever and youthful. Though native is less romantic and simpleton marriage is generally a good experience. Meena natives are advised to take care of needs and desires of marriage partner. Friends are abundant but often take undue advantage of natives kind and benevolent nature. Meena natives get on well with everyone including neighbors, friends, family and well wishers and not likely to make enemies out of people.</p>\r\n<p>Diseases: Meena natives have to deal with common problems like cough, cold, fever and flu quite often. Other common issues like frequent head pain and malaria are also possible. Meena natives may also have digestive problems like flatulence, indigestion and other common stomach problems. Obesity, Ulcers and Acne have also been observed.</p>\r\n<p>Limitations: Emotional, Habit of Procrastination, Lazy</p>', '', 1, 12, '2014-02-01 12:46:18', 899, '', '2014-05-08 07:21:28', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:46:18', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 11, 0, 'pisces sign, meena rashi, rashi ruled by guru', 'pisces in vedic astrology', 1, 81, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');
