(34, 146, 'Ashvini', 'ashvini', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ashvini Nakshatra is the first of the <a title="27 nakshatras link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> in the Cosmos which are studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of this Nakshatra are located in <a title="mesha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:aries&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Mesha Rashi</a>. Ashvini is ruled by <a title="ketu article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Ketu</a>. According to ancient vedic literature there are two gods by the name of Ashwini Kumars who are said to be the doctors of the Devtas (Vedic Gods) having vast knowledge of medicines. The name of Ashvini Nakshatra is derived from those gods. Symbol for Ashvini Nakshatra is a horse. Ashvini rules all forms of transport espeially speedy vehicles. Ashvini holds the vast knowledge of medicines and cures for ailments.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Males born under this nakshatra have good facial expressions. Eyes are large and bright. Forehead is broad and nose is a little bigger. Females born in this nakshatra have bright but small eyes like a fish. Ashvini Females have alluring looks and magnetic personality.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; General Events: Natives of Ashvini are spontaneous and like to get things done in a hurry. Ashvini Natives have an adventurous spirit that is blindely attracted to unknown challenges. They are competent workers who perform above average at the workplace. They are straight forward and prefer a no-nonsense approach in matters of business. Ashvini Natives have generally good health but sometimes suffer from bile complaints.</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Ashvini natives can have great careers as psychologists, therapist, physicians, music, horse trainers, jockeys, transport or as a race car driver. Education which leads to these mentioned careers is better if pursued. Having said that Ashvini Natives can be successful in almost all endeavours they take up and they are fond of literary pursuits. Period up to 30 years generally comes with a lot of struggles. Thereafter period between 30 to 55 years old sees gradual and steady progress being achieved.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Due to unrelenting behaviour Ashvini natvies are often subjected to harsh treatment by family especially the father. But inspite of such treatment, an Ashvini Native loves his family implicitly. There is a high chance of having a twin sibling for Ashvini Natives especially in Kumbha Lagna. Marriages for female natives generally takes place between 23 to 26 years while for males marriage takes place between 26 to 30 years of age. Natives are faithful to those who love them.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Natives of this nakshatra are hard working and diligent. They are not the type to leave a job at half way. They are focused and like to get on with things without fuzz. They are ideal people who can heal a person who is heart broken provided they are in the right frame of mind.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: They often have an unsteady mind and are quite short tempered. Their desire to extract revenge on their enemies at any cost is quite harmful. They are also fearless and stubborn who don''t think of results when they take on a task.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Since Ashvini is rule by Ketu praying to Lord Ganesha is ideal. Also wearing bright colors could help. Career in healing and medicine could make them have kindness and empathy for others.</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-01 12:49:33', 899, '', '2014-04-21 04:11:06', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-01 12:49:33', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 12, 26, 'ashvini nakhatra, ashwini nakshatra, ganda moola, ganda-moola nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by ketu', 'ashvini nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 40, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(35, 148, 'Bharani', 'bharani', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Bharani is the second among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. It is ruled by <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a> and all of the 4 Padas are located in <a title="mesha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:aries&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Mesha Rashi</a>. Gana of Bharani is human. Bharani is symbolized by an elephant and represents the female sexual organs. The devta which rules over Bharni is Yama who is also called Dharma.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Males born in this nakshatra have large forehead and less hair. Their height is medium-sized and they have beautiful teeth. If the birth is at noon then native could be very tall with a long neck and face. Females of this nakshatra have a good physique and white teeth.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Bharani is ruled by Shukra and located in the rashi of <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a>. This Mangal+Shukra combo ensures that native is over indulgent and extravagant in his lifestyle. Naturally it doesn''t go down well with those around. With the presiding deity being Dharma (Yama), the bharani native is bound to act on his own sense of justice. This native is unlikely to pursue a work which is wrong according to his conscience. Bharani Native is bound to face a lot of resistance and failures in his life. Bharani native is likely to spoil a good relationship over trivial matters and generally acts on his whims and fancies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Education and Career in Food and Beverages as well as hospitality sector is possible. Also other areas like administration, sports, music and occult science can give means of livelihood. Women can achieve a good career in sports industry. Though stability is rarely felt native does see progress in all sectors of life after 33 years of age. Native can be a good cosmetic surgeon or a judge. Cultivation of tobacco could also yield a good income.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Bharani natives like to dominate and do not like being dominated especially the female natives. Female natives enjoy love and satisfaction from her husband but is troubled by in-laws. Bharani natives love their family and do not like separation from their families. Male natives are blessed with wise and beautiful life partner. Marriage for females take around 23 years while marriage for males occurs around 27 years of age.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Females could have menstrual problems, uterus disorders, anemia while male natives may suffer from heart problems and lung problems due to smoking. Other possible diseases include fever, body pain and diabetes.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Bharani natives have an attractive personality and beautiful looks. People are often influenced by their poise and approach. They do not like to pretend . They rarely attract conflict and try to solve conflicts through peaceful means, tact and diplomacy.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Natives are fond of partying and over indulgent in luxurious ways. They are quite majestic and behave impulsively.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying Shiva, Yama or Kali. For females praying any goddess which denotes happiness, family and prosperity is advised.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:08:55', 899, '', '2014-04-21 04:19:07', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:08:55', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 9, 25, 'bharani nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by shukra', 'bharani nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 28, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(36, 150, 'Krittika', 'krittika', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Krittika is the 3rd nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 nakshtras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. Krittika is ruled by <a title="surya article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Surya</a> and symbolized by an axe. Among the 4 Padas the 1st Pada of Krittika is in <a title="mesha article article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=22:aries&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Mesha Rashi</a> while the remaining 3 Padas are in <a title="vrisabha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:taurus&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Vrishabha Rashi</a>. The gana of Krittika is Rakshasha and presiding god is Agni. According to popular texts the 6 stars in Krittika Nakshatra are said to be mothers of Kartikeyan. It is also suggested that Kartikeyan got his name from his six mothers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Males and Females have medium height. They have a thick neck along with a stout and solid body. Males have well-developed muscles.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Natives who belong to the 1st Pada of Krittika Nakshatra show the aggressive qualities of <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a> while the other 3 Padas show steady and calm attitude of Vrishabha Rashi. Often both males and females are arrogant and freedom loving. They have few friends due to their ego. Krittika natives do not like criticism levelled at them. Female natives are quite quarrelsome. If Surya is in good condition then natives are endowed with enhanced stamina and conviction to pursue goals. Otherwise Krittika natives rarely pursue any hobby or task for long. They do not think of consequences when they start a task. Not pursuing task till the end result in loss and failures.</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Krittika Natives can work in any sector but rarely ever master any sector of work. Natives often work away from hometown. Partnership is not suitable for them due to ego and arrogant nature. Ideal to work in government jobs but business in meat import/export, fashion design, hair stylist and medical especially autopsy is recommended. Both male and female natives can be good administrators if other planets are in favorable location.</p>\r\n<p>Family life: Males often marry a good wife who is devoted and dedicated. Wife is likely an effective administrator at home. Native''s wife may face health issues and sometimes their wife separate from natives due to unforeseen circumstances. Life upto 50 years is full of hardships. For male natives love marriage in indicated and often to a family friend. For females there maybe late marriage or divorce due to arrogant attitude and fierce nature. Ultimately result of separation and secluded life is a possible scenario for female natives of Krittika Nakshatra. Taking care of anger and frustration is advised for Krittika Females.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Female natives may suffer from physical and mental ailments due to excessive work. Tuberculosis, Gastric Problems, Piles, Brain Fever, Boils, Accidents and Wounds are possible for natives of Krittika Nakshatra.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Natives are self motivated, bright and honor their commitments. They are courageous and ambitious.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Natives are often stubborn and have an unstable mind. They are aggressive and arrogant and often pursue unrealistic dreams.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Kartikeya and Surya. Also chanting Gayatri Mantra is advised.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:13:46', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:55:08', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:13:46', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 24, 'krittika nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by surya', 'krittika in vedic astrology', 1, 37, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(37, 152, 'Rohini', 'rohini', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Rohini is the fourth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category links" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. The gana of Rohini is human and all the 4 Padas of Rohini are in <a title="vrisabha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:taurus&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Vrishabha Rashi</a>. Rohini is ruled by <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> and the presiding deity is Brahma who is the creator of the Universe. Rohini is symbolized by a chariot pulled by two oxen. In Vedic Texts it is mentioned that Rohini was the most favorite wife of Chandra among the 27 nakshatras (all married to Chandra) and Chandra''s impartial love towards Rohini and neglecting of other wives led Daksha Prajapati to curse Chandra.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Both males and females natives of Rohini have attractive eyes and graceful appearance. Males have a slender physique and females have a fair complexion. They are loved and honored due to their charming personality.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Rohini is ruled by Chandra and located in Vrishabha which is a rashi ruled by <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a>. Naturally the Rohini natives are emotional and attracted to finer things in life. They are highly imaginative and lovers or art, music, dance and sculptures. They have a charming and attractive personality yet can be quite stubborn at times. Generally both males and females are very sensitive and extra caution is advised when dealing with them. Rohini natives have a restless mind and keeping focus on a single activity is next to impossible for them. Rohini natives think with their hearts and not with their heads. This is why they can be easily manipulated. Females are well dressed and well behaved but often short tempered and violent when instigated. They have a panache to show off. Rohini natives are happy and satisfied and generally do not hold grudges in life.</p>\r\n<p>Education &amp; Profession: Decent Education is suggested. Rohini natives can be successful in both business and jobs. Career related to arts, fashion, sweet and juicy foods as well as materials and cosmetics is favorable. Agriculture especially growth of juicy fruits and vegetables can yield a good income. Extra caution is advised when going for business partnership for Rohini natives. Due to their emotional, kind and simple nature there is a high probability that Rohini natives can be manipulated in business partnership. Generally natives are honest, sincere and truthful at their workplace.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives are more attached to mothers and mothers relatives. Males and Females have good life partners and children. Natives are happy and satisfied due to kind and caring nature as well as the penchant for not holding any grudges. Natives are loved and honoured by their society due to being honest, sincere and gentle. Though sometimes stubborn and emotional nature causes problems for Rohini natives. Females are advised to avoid suspicion of their partners.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Males natives can have harmonal imbalances due to mental stress. Diseases connected to blood and water are a possibility. Females are likely to suffer from irregular menses and pain in breasts.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Lord Brahma or Lord Shiva is quite beneficial. Since Lord Krishna was born in this nakshtra and nakshatra is in a rashi of shukra holding fasts on friday and praying to lord krishna could also provide beneficial results.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:14:21', 899, '', '2014-04-21 04:37:11', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:14:21', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 23, 'rohini nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by chandra', 'rohini nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 37, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(38, 154, 'Mrigashira', 'mrigashira', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mrigashirsha (also called Mrigashira) is the fifth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. It is located in the Orion Constellation. Of the 4 Padas, the first 2 Padas are located in <a title="vrisabha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=23:taurus&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Vrishabha Rashi</a> while the remaining 2 Padas are in <a title="mithuna rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=24:gemini&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Mithuna Rashi</a>. The symbol for Mrigashirsha is an antelope''s head while the gana is devta and the presiding deity is <a title="chandra rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a>. Mrigashirsha is rule by <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Mrigashira natives born in Vrishabha are slightly fairer as compared to Mrigashira natives born in Mithuna. They are physically delicate and quite nervous and restless. They possess a stout body, tall height and moderate complexion along with thin legs and long arms. Females have the more or less the same physical attributes as males. In addition to them Mrigashira females are sharp with a lean body with a good face and facial expressions.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Natives are happy-go-lucky with a good sense of humour and quick wit. They enjoy communication both verbal and written. They are spontaneous, enthusiastic and love socializing. They are quite suspicious and can sense danger. Generally they love lothing and accessories. They have good grasping abilities and can can learn and adapt very quickly. They have a creative nature but take time when they are placed in difficult situation. Mrigashira females like to control their hushand. They are sincere in their dealings and expect the same from others. Blind trust on others leads to frustration, repentance and feeling of being cheated. They turn quite impatient when confontrated with prejudice. Generally life upto 32 years sees problems in settling down. Mrigashira natives born is vrishabha tend to float career paths before finally settling down. Mrigashira natives born in Mithuna can make a good career in accountancy. Besides that poetry, astrology, engineering, teaching and administration are suggested. Mrigashira females are alert, quick-witted but have a poisonous tongue. She is educated and fond of arts. Period upto 32 years is generally slow for career while the period from 33 to 50 years sees maximum career growth and satisfaction. Extra precaution is required to see money is not wasted in later years of life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life- Despite of having innocent intentions and noble heart, Mrigashira natives rarely enjoy good sibling relationship. Spouse doesn''t keep a good health. There are problems in marital life due to suspicion and quirky humour aimed at spouse. Females are dominant over husbands. Females are very likely to have one or two affairs prior to marriage.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Sharp intelligence, strong individuality, witty, enthusiastic, quick learner, youthful and sensual.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Flirty, impulsvie, fickle minded, need constant attention and sensitive to criticism.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Mrigashira natives suffer from acidity, constipation and shoulder problems in general. Females may also suffer from goiter, pimples, venereal diseases and menstrual troubles.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Mrigashira Natives are advised to pray to Chandra and Goddess Parvati.</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:15:03', 899, '', '2014-04-21 04:39:36', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:15:03', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 12, 22, 'mrigashira nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by mangal', 'mrigashira in vedic astrology', 1, 41, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(39, 156, 'Ardra', 'ardra', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ardra is the sixth naksthatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 nakshatras</a>. All the 4 Padas are located in <a title="mithuna rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=24:gemini&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Mithuna Rashi</a>. The ruling planet is <a title="rahu article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Rahu</a> while the symbol for Ardra is a human head. The presiding diety is Rudra. Gana of Ardra is Manushya. Since Rahu rules Ardra and location is in Mithuna which is the house of <a title="budh article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:budh&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Budh</a> &amp; Rahu the natives have been shown to have characteristics of both Rahu &amp; Budh.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Attributes: Large face, curly hair and sullen expressions have been observed. Though any fixed physical trait is difficult to associate with Ardra natives owing to the mysterious nature of Rahu.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Ardra natives are determined in their responsibilities and get the job done by any means necessary. Moral and Values often take a back seater and success by hook or crook gains precedence. Career in politics is ideal for Ardra natives. There is high probability that native is in politics or politically well connected. Due to Rahu being a karaka for foreign lands, Ardra natives have also been seen to settle abroad and earn their living on foreign lands. Ardra natives are active thinkers and can change personality as the situation demands. Many times they become arrogant, impolite and sarcastic. But mostly they are caring and concerned for others well-being. Due to Ardra location in rashi of Budh there are times when Ardra natives tend to talk a lot on a wide range of topics. Special care is required not to spill out secrets.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; They have special attraction for opposite sex and crave for materialistic lifestyle. Career in profession related to mysteries or solving mysteries like detective, occult subjects, hypnotism, psychology and other less known subjects are ideal. Ardra females in addition to the above mentioned traits are also extravagant in their lifestyle. Female natives can attain good knowledge in a wide range of fields. Period between 32 to 42 years is golden period for ardra natives both male and female.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Marriage can be delayed for both the male and female natives. If married early marital fights are possible. Divorce is also possible if marriage takes early. Children can also prove to be source of unease and unhappiness.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Mysterious diseases whose cure is not readily available are possible for Ardra natives. Paralysis, Heart troubles, shoulder problems, asthma are observed in ardra natives. Kidney troubles and diseases of the urinal system are also possible for both males and females.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Curious mind, hunger for success and knowledge, quick in action, good communication skills and vocational skills. Compassionate for suffering</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Arrogant, abuses power, mischievous, excessive indulgence, ungrateful and prone to use illegal or anti-social means to achieve success</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to lord shiva is advised who is always content and calm.</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:16:30', 899, '', '2014-07-21 08:58:18', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:16:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 13, 21, 'ardra nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by rahu', 'ardra nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 40, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(40, 158, 'Punarvasu', 'punarvasu', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Punarvas is the 7th nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 nakshatras</a>. The benevolent <a title="guru article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Guru</a> is the ruling planet, presiding diety is Aditi who is known as earth goddess and according to Vedic text was the mother of all devtas. Lord Ram was born in this nakshatra in Karka rashi. Of the 4 Padas the first 3 Padas are in <a title="mithuna rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=24:gemini&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Mithuna Rashi</a> while the remaining last pada is in <a title="karka rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:cancer&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Karka Rashi</a>. Word ''Punarvasu'' is derived from words ''Punar'' and ''Vasu'' which means ''Again'' and ''Live'' respectively. In broad terms Punarvasu signifies to Rise Again, to be Reborn.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Native have good height and oval face. Punarvasu natives tend to be obese in later years of life. Male natives are handsome with long thighs. Some sort of identification mark is present on face or back of the head. Females have curly hair, prominent nonse and sweet speech.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Punarvasu natives are well content in life due to benevolent Guru being the lord of this nakshatra. They generally refrain from illegal/criminal activities to attain their objective. They are simple and straight forward. They have complete faith in god and inclined to follow their religion. They are eager to serve the needy and do not like to cause trouble for others. Generally they have a good education. Owing to their simple nature and content in life they are only moderately successful but rarely suffer from poverty. Females are successful in everything they do. Business partnership is ill-advised for Punarvasu natives. Though wealth maybe moderate, public reputation and dignity is high. Period upto 32 years is difficult. They have special ability to rise up from calamities and no sort of calamity can keep them down for long. They can have successful career in acting, teaching, drama, politics, writing, publishing, philosophical work, working as a scientist and psychologist.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Punarvasu natives are the most obedient among the siblings. They have great respect for their parents and elders. They have a good circle of friends. For males a good partner is indicated though the partner may be prone to sickness. Friction in marriage or with family members is indicated for male natives. For females the partner is caring and doting and children are loving. Female natives generally enjoy good family life. House remains orderly.</p>\r\n<p>Health: No major health concern is indicated apart from gastric problems for Punarvasu natives.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Caring, loving, nurturing, simple lifestyle, satisfaction in life, friendly and religious</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Unstable in relationship especially males, lack of foresight in business owing to simple nature.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Punarvasu natives should pray to Goddess Laxmi.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:17:15', 899, '', '2014-07-21 08:58:36', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:17:15', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 16, 19, 'punarvasu nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by guru', 'punarvasu nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 36, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(41, 160, 'Pushya', 'pushya', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Pushya nakshatra is the eight nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 nakshatras</a>&nbsp;in Vedic Astrology. The word ''Pushya'' means nourishment and accordingly this nakshatra replenishes, nourishes and reinvigorates. Pushya is regarded as the best among the 27 nakshatras. All the auspicious undertakings or purchase of jewelry are done when <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> enters Pushya Nakshatra. Pushya is ruled by <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">shani</a> and its symbol is cow''s udder. The gana is devta and the presiding deity is Brihaspati or <a title="guru rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Guru</a>. All the 4 Padas of Pushya are in <a title="karka rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:cancer&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Karka Rashi</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Pushya natives are difficult to discern based on physical characteristics. Since the nakshatra is ruled by Shani, situated in Karka which is Chandra''s rashi and presiding diety is Guru a lot of anomalies are seen in physical traits. Sometimes males are observed to be tall and thin while woman are noticed to be short with an oval face.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Pushya natives are hard working and dedicated to their work. They have a helping nature. The nakshatra of Shani brings control and organization in life of natives through difficult circumstances in early childhood. Poverty is possible upto 15 or 16 years of life. Generally hardships and dependency in early life moulds pushya natives character and they become independent, organized, hard working, sincere and honest individuals. They can work with patience and calm towards achievement of a goal. Careful consideration is required to not overtake a business or project without careful thinking otherwise the desired result may not be ideal. As the natives learn more through experience it is not necessary for them to opt for a difficult course. Hard work and dedication often makes them over burdened at work place. Extra care is required not to overdo things and concentrate on doing the task allocated without getting into the nitty gritty details. As long as skills and abilities are assessed before proceding to work, nothing shall be impossible for the natives. Another impeccable quality is their honesty which does not let them take criminal or illegal tasks. Females apart from qualities mentioned above have peaceful and submissive nature. Pushya natives both males and females cannot properly handle negative criticism or positive feedback.</p>\r\n<p>Family life- Pushya natives are quite attached to their parents. They become independent when they grow up. Spouse for pushya males natives should be self sufficient and with a conservative thinking, dress sense. Females are submissive and cannot express themselves freely. This leads partners to doubt them. Females are devoted and amicable by nature. Both male and female natives have a problem with expressing themselves due to Shani (restrictions) ruling the rashi of Chandra which controls emotions they have difficulties in family life. Many a times natives have to live away from family.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Hard working, help others, good advisers, honest, dedicated and liked by others.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Insecure, Problems in expressing themselves, dogmatic, over sensitive</p>\r\n<p>Health: Shani is dry and cold while Chandra&nbsp;(ruler of Karka Rashi) rules all the bodily fluids. Thereby problems related to body fluids like hormonal problems, cough, cold, asthma or other problems related to Kapha Dosha are possible.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Lord Vishnu is advised for pushya natives.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:22:16', 899, '', '2014-04-21 04:54:55', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:22:16', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 9, 20, 'nakshatra ruled by shani, pushya nakshatra', 'pushya nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 49, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(42, 162, 'Ashlesha', 'ashlesha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ashlesha is the ninth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatras category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 nakshatras</a>&nbsp;studied in Vedic Astrology. It is ruled by <a title="budh article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:budh&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Budh</a>&nbsp;and all the 4 Padas are located in <a title="karka rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=25:cancer&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Karka rashi</a>. The symbol for Ashlesha is a coiled snake and presiding diety is Naga. According to Valmiki Ramayan the twin brothers Laxman and Shatrughan were born in this nakshatra.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Natives have a pentrating glare which can hyponitize and mesmerize its prey, very much like a snake. Also they have an intriguing speech and a way with words. They have a stout body and brownish complexion. They do not have much resistance power. Looks are not the most attractive either.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Natives have to accept responsibility at a very young age due to parents not alive or abandoning the native. This makes the native very possesive in nature for other relationship as he can''t stand the sight to lose them. Inspite of emotional insecurities the natives can be quite self-centred. They make quite good politicians with their mezmerizing body language and attractive speeches. Ofcourse Ashlesha natives are more associated with cunning, deceit and corrupt so you rarely see honest administrators in this nakshatra. They are often deceitful and can be quite cruel sometimes. Native is emotionally insecure and seldom suffer from mental diseases like schizophrenia and paranoia. Too much of suspicion in life invites all sorts of mental worries. While they are open to criticizing others they do not welcome personal criticism. Career in Politics, as a Physician, Psychologist, Applied Medicines, Chemical Engineer, Chemist and in Sex Rackets is possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Often abandoned by parents at early age when Ashlesha nakshatra is in lagna. Chandra in ashlesha makes a native insecure and sometimes leads to suspicion and worries. Natives over possessive nature becomes a problem in relationship. <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in ashlesha makes a native insecure and sometimes leads to suspicion and worries. Native is not able to give the space needed for a relationship to thrive Too much criticism and poisonous tongue can also damage relationship. Unable to co-exist in surrounding environment.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Learned, Mesmerizing, Leadership Qualities.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Mental Instability, Deceitful, Possessive, Secretive and Talkative.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Mental disease are possible for Ashlesha natives. Also flatulence and stomach problems possible.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: For the suspicious nature, poisonous tongue and mental insecurities praying to Lord Shiva is best. To calm the talkative and manipulative nature prayers to Lord Ram or Lord Vishnu are advised.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:23:50', 899, '', '2014-04-21 04:58:35', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:23:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 12, 18, 'ashlesha nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by budh', 'ashlesha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 37, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(43, 164, 'Magha', 'magha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Magha is the tenth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Magha are situated in the rashi of Simha (ruled by Surya) and Magha is ruled by Ketu. In accordance with it Magha natives have qualities of both <a title="surya article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Surya</a> and <a title="ketu article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Ketu</a> endowed. Magha''s symbol is a royal throne which symbolizes power, status and prestige. Magha''s gana is Daitya/Rakshasha while its presiding diety are the forefathers. Surya''s placement in Magha between 1 and 10 ( = degree) indicates it is in its Mool Trikona position. This placement makes Surya feel like an emperor which can grant gifts and benediction. Magha comes under the category of Ganda Moola Nakshatra.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Magha natives are endowed with qualities of both Surya and Ketu. Magha natives are powerful, influential and short tempered. But at the same time they are spiritual and quite generous. Magha natives are optimistic and free spirited. Magha natives obtain fame which can last through generations. Magha females have a frank and courageous nature. At the same time they are charming and have an interesting personality. These qualities invite many fr-enemies. Female natives love their family and can go to any lengths to safeguard their families interest. Such actions can be used by fr-enemies against Magha Females.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Males have a proud and arrogant nature and command respect from their peers. Public status and financial dignity are generally secure for magha natives. Magha natives respect their elders and are god fearing. They are generous and donate money for noble causes and philanthropic activities. Although Magha natives achieve quite good status and wealth they are better off not to pursue an individual business. Their straight forward nature and generous character can lead to loss making in business. This applies for both male and female natives born with <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Magha. Magha natives are the ideal middle man or coordinators in work place. Career in top management position is a good option. Also career in politics, law and career as coordinators and brokers is viable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Magha males have good and faithful wife. Females are religious minded and devoted to their husbands. Inspite of that their simple and straight forward nature invites frictions in marriage and family life. Even in the modern day world there are places where woman raising her voice and giving a frank opinion is not invited. Normally both male and female natives have very few friends.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Magha natives may suffer from burns, boils and piles. Night blindness and eye problems are also a possibility.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Dependable and Smooth Coordinators</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Arrogant, Hot Tempered, Susceptible to Criticism and Flattery.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Performing religious yagnas and Shradha for obtaining blessings of forefathers.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:24:19', 899, '', '2014-04-21 08:58:58', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:24:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 8, 17, 'magha nakshatra, ganda moola nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by ketu', 'magha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 33, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');
