(44, 166, 'Purva Phalguni', 'purva-phalguni', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Purva Phalguni is the eleventh nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatras category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Purva Phalguni are in <a title="simha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:leo&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Simha Rashi</a> and the ruling planet is <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a>. Gana is Manushya/Human and the Presiding diety is Bhaga who is one of the 12 Adityas. Symbol for Purva Phalguni is a swinging hammock (Jhula).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;This nakshatra is called Bhagadaivata Star. All the good things in life like pleasure, prosperity, love, enjoyment and sensual blessings are possible through blessings of this nakshatra. A nakshatra ruled by Shukra in the rashi of <a title="surya article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Surya</a> is precipice for good fortune, luck and prosperity.&nbsp;<span style="color: #333333; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;"><span><br /></span></span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Purva Phalguni females have an oval face and well built figure. They are soft and cultured but prone to arrogance. Males have a healthy constitution, attractive personality and mixed color. Purva Phalguni Natives both males and females are energetic and restless.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Natives have a strong desire to be liked and noticed by others. They are fond of music and arts. They generally avoid conflicts and disputes and try to solve conflicts peacefully through tact. Natives like to travel to places where weather is clear and bright like sunny beaches or mountains. Natives enjoy freedom and do not like working under subordination. If employed at a workplace, the tend to change their jobs frequently until 45 years of age. Period after 45 years of age sees power and authority. They generally oppose to getting benefits at the cost of others. Natives like to be clean and tidy. Purva Phalguni natives are better off with starting their own business venture or earning an independent livelihood through arts or music. It is difficult for natives to learn new things as their scope is limited to earning fame and fortune. Career as Actors, Models, Musicians, Retail Sales, Travel Agents, Cosmetics, Jewelry, Wedding Planners, Sex Therapist and Marriage Counselor is possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Both male and female natives enjoy happiness and enjoyment in married life. Both the life partner and children provide happiness to individuals. Love marriage is more likely compared to arranged marriage. Native resides away from birth place and family members. Purva Phalguni natives have a good circle of friends and are quite popular in their group. Extra-marital affairs is a possible scenario for Purva Phalguni natives.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Creative, Intelligent, Charming, Carefree, Open Minded, Refined, Youthful</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Indulgent, Impulsive, Promiscuous Nature, Narcissism.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Dental problems are possible.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Prayers to Goddess Laxmi. Seva and Pooja of Shiva Linga is also beneficial.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:25:41', 899, '', '2014-07-21 09:00:05', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:25:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 15, 16, 'purvaphalguni nakshatra, purva phalguni nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by shukra', 'purva phalguni nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 37, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(45, 168, 'Uttara Phalguni', 'uttara-phalguni', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Uttara Phalguni is the twelfth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. The gana for Uttara Phalguni is Manushya/Human while the ruling planet is <a title="surya article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Surya</a>. Presiding diety is Aryaman and the symbol is a bed. The 1st Pada of this nakshatra is located in <a title="simha rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=26:leo&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Simha rashi</a> while the remaining 3 Padas are located in <a title="kanya rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:virgo&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Kanya rashi</a>. In accordance the natives with Chandra in 1st Pada show characteristics of Surya like arrogance, leadership skills and intolerant nature while the natives with <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in the remaining 3 Padas show characteristics of Budh like chatty and articulate nature.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features; Natives of Uttara Phalguni have some sort of prominent mark like black mole on neck or face. Male natives are tall and chubby with large face and long nose. Women born in Uttara Phalguni have a soft voice. Natives born in 1st Pada of Uttara Phalguni have good health and eyesight as well as attractive eyes.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Uttara Phalguni natives are born social workers. They are quite helpful to their friends, family and generally to all in need. While natives of the 1st Pada maybe arrogant and proud due to the combination of Surya Nakshatra (Uttara Phalguni ) + Surya rashi (Simha), the natives born in other 3 Padas are simple and straight forward. While natives of 1st Pada maybe irritating they do get high position in life. It has been observed that females can make quite a good career as actress if they are born when 1st Pada of Uttara Phalguni is in lagna/ascendent. Natives of 1st Pada are hot tempered while the natives of other 3 Padas which fall in Kanya rashi resolve conflicts through discussion. Uttara Phalguni natives often see meaningful progress after 38 years of life have passed. Uttara Phalguni natives can have wonderful career as Social Worker, Philantrophist, Actors, Mathematician, Astrologers and Astronomers.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Generally for male natives in Uttara Phalguni married life possesses little or no friction. Women can get a good partner and children. Women are good in managing matters of domestic life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Ambitious, Good Communicator, Generous</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Ego, Stubborn and Over-giving</p>\r\n<p>Health: Health remains good with no major complications unless some bad placement in horoscope is present.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Surya and chanting of the Gayatri Mantra.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:26:26', 899, '', '2014-07-21 09:00:27', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:26:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 11, 15, 'uttaraphalguni nakshatra, uttara phalguni nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by surya', 'uttara phalguni nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 42, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(46, 170, 'Hasta', 'hasta', '<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Hasta is the the thirteenth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatras category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas are located in <a title="kanya rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:virgo&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Kanya rashi</a>. The gana is devta and the presiding diety is Savitr who is one of the 12 Adityas. Hasta Nakshatra is ruled by <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> and located in the rashi of <a title="budh article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:budh&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Budh</a>. This awkward Budh-Chandra relationship can sometimes cause nervous disorders as Budh (rules the nervous system) and Chandra (rules the mind and thoughts) are planetary enemies.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Appearance: Female natives can be chubby with a fat stomach and prominent chest region. Males though typically less attractive make up with an attractive personality. Both male and female natives could be tall with scar on upper right hand or below shoulders.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Hasta females have a warm but lazy character. Hasta females only work when required but handle task cheerfully and with energy. Female natives are generally cheerful and do not stay angry for long. Hasta males are clever, witty and entertaining. They like to keep company of females. Hasta natives of both gender are a great company to have. Natives are unable to adapt to new technology and thoughts and prefer the old traditions and customs. Hasta natives get respect and honor from public. There is a possibility for fluctuations in life through mental, physical and social factors.&nbsp; Moderate success is observed for natives with&nbsp; help coming from unexpected quarters. Natives are better to pursue a career in business and can make good advisers. A good all round knowledge is observed in the natives and capability to solve disputes peacefully is a trait among natives. Period from 30 to 42 years is golden period of life. Career as craftsmen, Artist, Writers, Painters, Teachers, Adviser, Volunteer Work. Hospital Staff, Counselors, Astrologer, Travel Industry and Comedians is possible.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Hasta natives have a tendency to give parental guidance especially in a relationship. They do not see their partner as their equal but rather someone who needs parenting. Marriage for Hasta Natives is more satisfying in later years. Partner is simple and capable. No major problems are indicated in married life unless there are other bad planetary combinations or aspect.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Natives may suffer from bad health especially cough and cold. Females may also suffer from rheumatism and piles.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Creative, Humorous, Practical and Pleasant Personality</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Emotional instability and Bad Health</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Hasta natives should pray to Surya.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:26:57', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:13:24', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:26:57', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 14, 14, 'hasta nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by chandra', 'hasta nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 24, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(47, 172, 'Chitra', 'chitra', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Chitra Nakshatra is the fourteenth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatras category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> in Vedic Astrology. The first 3 Padas are located in <a title="kanya rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=27:virgo&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Kanya rashi</a> while the fourth and last pada is located in <a title="tula rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=28:libra&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Tula rashi</a>. The gana for Chitra is Daitya while the symbol is an oyster with a pearl in it. <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a> is the ruling planet for Chitra nakshatra and the presiding diety is Vishwakarma who is the god of all creation. Ideally a nakshatra of warrior Mangal in the rashi of talkative <a title="budh article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:budh&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Budh</a> or extravagant <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a> is not ideal. Yet this natives learn with time and gain extraordinary success especially those born with <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Kanya rashi. Chitra lagna is considered auspicious for males but inauspicious for females.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Chitra natives have a lean body. They maybe stout and tall sometimes.</p>\r\n<p>Character/Events: Chitra males are clever, successful, dexterous and direct in speech. Females are fickle with men, competitive and even selfish in some cases. Chitra females with Chandra in Tula rashi are expensive and luxurious. They are fond of perfumes, cosmetics and expensive items. Extra marital relationship is possible due to the Mangal+Shukra relationship. Chitra females born with Chandra in Kanya are a bit masculine and athletic.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Chitra males are thoughful and profound in approach. They are great with machines and tools be it mechanical or surgical equipments. Kanya born chitra natives are creative while Tula born chitra natives are more artistic and like music, acting etc. Period between 33 years and 54 years of age will be golden period for native. Chitra natives are fantastic planners. They have ideal career as Software or Hardware Professionals. They can also make good surgeons. In addition they can make a successful career in army planning and intelligence, real estate developers and tula born natives can also become actors, designers and musicians.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives derive love and respect from their siblings and parents but sometimes difference of opinion is possible with family members. Generally Chitra natives live separate from home and family members. Native enjoy a great repo with mother and get gains from mothers relatives. Married life is not cordial and frictions are possible. Though divorce is unlikely unless other inauspicious yoga are present.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Difficulty in internal organs especially kidneys and bladder as well as tumors and appendicitis.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Artistic, Independent, Innovative Thinkers and Intelligent Planners</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Quarrelsome, Critical (in kanya rashi), Immoral and Spendthrift (in tula rashi)</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Praying to Goddess Durga.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:27:26', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:15:02', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:27:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 11, 13, 'chitra nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by mangal', 'chitra nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 28, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(48, 174, 'Swati', 'swati', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Swati is the fifteenth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatras category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> studied in Vedic Astrology. Swati is ruled by Rahu and the presiding deity is Vayu. All the 4 Padas are located in Tula rashi and the gana for swati is devta. Though <a title="tula rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=28:libra&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Tula Rashi</a> is the rashi of balance, <a title="rahu article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=8:rahu&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Rahu</a> creates imbalance and unrest in the lives of Swati natives. Unless <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shani</a> is involved the inner feelings and outer behavior of Swati natives tends to be poles apart.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Natives both males and females are attractive and alluring. Females have a distinguished speech and manner of walking.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Swati natives have mysterious behavior. The outward calm and composed demeanor due to Tula Rashi''s balanced persona is hindered by the inner turmoil and uneasy feelings brought forth by Rahu who always wants more. Swati natives cannot stay at one place and like to travel as and when they please. While Rahu encourages taboo breaking activities which are anti-social and unlawful the balancing view of Tula rarely allows that side to be in public view. They may be enticed to pursue taboo activities in secret but outwardly they love to show simplicity and good mannerisms. Generally Swati females have a truthful and straight forward character. While males are thoughtful and slow in their actions they are brilliant at analyzing work based on intelligence and logic. Swati males are religious and somewhat orthodox. Swati natives are peace loving but prone to be hot tempered and revengeful when instigated. They are adamant in their views and independent in their approach. They do not level criticism at others and cannot handle criticism leveled at them. Period after 30 years sees growth in business and professional sector. Swati natives have ideal career in travelling sector, pharmacist, diplomats, gold smith and politicians (if Shani is involved).</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Swati natives do not have an ideal married life. While the outer picture is a happy married life the inner reality is different. Native may have no stability in matters of money and place of accommodation.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Mysterious conditions possible due to Swati being a nakshatra of Rahu.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Business Minded, Friendly, Independent.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Hot Temper</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Swati natives should pray to Saraswati and Bhairav (Avatar of Rudra). &nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:30:30', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:17:53', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:30:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 12, 12, 'swati nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by rahu', 'swati nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 26, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(49, 176, 'Vishakha', 'vishakha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Vishakha Nakshatra is the sixteenth nakshatra among <a title="27 nakshatras category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> in Vedic Astrology. While the first 3 Padas are located in <a title="tula rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=28:libra&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Tula Rashi</a> the last pada of Vishakha is in <a title="vrischika rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=29:scorpio&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Vrischika Rashi</a>. The presiding diety for Vishakha are Indra and Agni while the gana is Rakhshasa. The ruling planet is the benevolent <a title="guru article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=5:guru&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Guru</a>. Vishakha is also called Anuradha which is the birth star of <a title="surya article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=1:surya&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Surya</a> while it is also called Radha who is known as the consort of Lord Krishna. Vishakha has the nature of its deities Indra and Agni which is full of splendor and vigor albeit for a short period of time.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Vishakha natives are round, bright and physical appearance is attractive. Some natives are obese and tall while others have a short and lean structure. Vishaksha females have delicate features and a soft and pleasing voice but underneath the delicacy likes a very strong character.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Vishakha natives are full of vigor and vitality and possess intelligence of the highest order. They are firm believers in God but do not believe in orthodox principles or age old traditions. They are fond of adopting modern ideas. They treat all religion, caste and creed as equal. Vishakha natives are also impatient, aggressive and quite quarrelsome. They are quite active but not so much popular. Their aggressive behavior is disliked by others. Also they have lot of pride and are easily offended. They may have enemies due to hot temper and arrogant nature. Natives born in Tula rashi in the first 3 Padas have strong diplomatic skills. Natives sometimes are spendthrift while other times they are stingy in spending. Vishakha natives are best advised to do independent business or high responsibility jobs. Career as Psychologist, Medical Diagnosis, Counseling, Investigative Journalism and Scientific Research is best suited. Due to good oratary skill natives could also be good Politicians.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Vishakha females are quite appealing to opposite sex and generally have a fortunate marriage. Husband is good natured and wealthy. Female natives are likely to have very few children. Female natives are fond of travels and travel often with their partners. Vishakha natives have more enemies as compared to friends. Vishakha natives do not get appropriate love or care from mother owing to death of mother or other unforseen circumstances. Although they respect their father very much and father also is the more doting of the two parents there are bound to be differences with father. This makes the natives hard working and self made individuals since childhood. Although they love their partners they are prone to addictions or extra-marital affairs. These traits cause problems in family and social life.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Health remains normally good but natives are prone to paralytic attack especially after 55 years of age. Ashthma is also observed among natives.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Intelligent, Spiritual, Good Communicator.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Quarrelsome, Restless and Aggressive.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Remdies: Praying to Lord Krishna and Lord Shiva</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:31:14', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:21:09', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:31:14', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 10, 11, 'vishakha nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by guru', 'vishakha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 29, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(50, 178, 'Anuradha', 'anuradha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Anuradha is the seventeenth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category links" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 nakshatras</a> in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Anuradha are in <a title="vrischika rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=29:scorpio&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Vrischika Rashi</a> and the presiding diety is Mitra who is one of the 12 Adityas. Symbol for Anuradha is a lotus flower and the gana is devta. Anuradha is ruled by <a title="shani article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=7:shani&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shani</a> and located in Vrischika Rashi which is ruled by <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangal</a>. Shani and Mangal are polar opposites in terms of personality. Natives with <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> in Anuradha take time to learn to balance between the negativity of Shani and impatience of Mangal. Slowly they learn the art to apply Shani''s hard work and discipline to Mangal''s vigor and afterwards success follows.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Anuradha natives have a beautiful face and bright eyes. They have somewhat of a dejected look on their face due to the inner termoil of Shani-Mangal fight to dominate individuals personality. They are generally lean and tall.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Female natives are clever, witty and fun loving. They are surrounded by admiring circle of friends. Often they invite envy and malice from others who are jelous of them. Males are robust and healthy but derive very little enjoyment in life. While their speech shows warmth and kindness their inner heart is filled with malice. Due to their revengeful character there is no inner peace possible. Natives both male and females face several difficulties in life but can successfully overcome those obstacles. Natives are fim believer in God. These natives spend an independent life and start working at a very young age of 17 or 18. Life between 17 to 48 would be full of trials with some occassional benefits. But life after 48 years would be extremely good. Natives are best suited to pursue business but if employed they would get on quite well with superiors. Career in conflict resolutions, deal makers and negotiators would give maximum benefits.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives have strained relationship with parents and siblings. They live an independent life and generally settle abroad. Marital life is happy and a good partner is indicated. Children are successful if the native provides proper attention, care, love and affection to the children. Female natives are devoted to their partners and observe religious paractices sternly. She is generally devoted to in-laws and this trait gives her good rewards.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Natives are prone to cough and cold.</p>\r\n<p>Positive: Deal Maker. Friendly Appearance.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Revengeful, No Inner Peace</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Anuradha natives should worship the 12 Adityas and chant the Gayatri Mantra.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:32:08', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:27:37', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:32:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 11, 10, 'anuradha nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by shani', 'anuradha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 29, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(51, 180, 'Jyestha', 'jytestha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Jyestha is the eighteenth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> in Vedic Astrology. All the 4 Padas of Jyestha are in <a title="vrischika rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=29:scorpio&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Vrischika Rashi</a> while the presiding diety is Indra. The ruling planet is <a title="budh article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=4:budh&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Budh</a> and gana is Rakshasha. Symbol is an earring resembling Vishnu''s Sudrashan Chakra. Jyestha comes under the category of Gandmoola Nakshatra. Jyestha means the Eldest or Best in the family.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Natives have good physical stamina and attractive figure but teeth maybe defective.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Jyestha is located in Vrischika Rashi which is ruled by <a title="mangal article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=3:mangal&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Mangala</a> and nakshatra itself is ruled by Budh. Hence due to the Mangal-Budh relationship the natives are trustworthy but at the same time bound to be critical in speech. Jyestha natives thrive on being the main souce of financial income and social stability for the family. They understand the importance of time and are quite loyal to their responsibilities. They learn to adapt quickly to difficult situations. They are often restless and bound to make a mountain of a small mole. Natives are hot tempered and prone to stain good relationships. They generally occupy an influential position and command respect among others. They can rise to top ranks through their loyalty and sincere efforts. Period upto 50 years is full of trials. Period between 18 to 26 may see financial troubles or mental diseases. Period from 27 to 50 years offers some stability. Female natives are capable, dignified and self-sufficient. Female natives have capacity to become wealthy through independent efforts. They can pursue a successful career in business and service. They achieve top rank through their own efforts at their employment place.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives have limited or no relationship with parents and siblings. While they are appreciated for bringing financial and social stability inspite of &nbsp;troubles they are often resented for their temper, intolerance and criticism of others. Married life is harmonious but separation maybe possible due to unforeseen circumstances. Partner is likely to have a demanding nature.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Bread Winner for family, Self Made Individuals</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Anger and Ego, Control Freaks, Restless</p>\r\n<p>Health: Cough and Cold</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Jyestha natives are advised to pray to Lord Vishnu due to the Mangal-Budh relationship and also perform the ''Moola Shanti'' pooja for the Gandmoola Dosha.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:35:20', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:46:11', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:35:20', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 12, 9, 'jyestha nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by budh', 'jyestha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 17, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(52, 182, 'Mula', 'mula', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Mula Nakshatra is the ninteenth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshatras</a> in Vedic Astrology. Mula means root in Sanskrit. The planetary lord of Mula Nakshatra is <a title="ketu article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=9:ketu&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Ketu</a>. All the 4 Padas of Mula are in <a title="dhana rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=30:sagittarius&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Dhana Rashi</a> while the symbol for Mula are a bunch of roots tied together. The gana is Rakshasha and the presiding deity is Nirriti who is the goddess of destruction. It falls under the category of Gand Moola Nakshatra. Vedic Some astrology texts advises people not to take loans or grants when <a title="chandra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=2:chandra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Chandra</a> is in Mula Nakshatra as they would be unable to pay the debt back.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Natives have good physical features with bright eyes and beautiful limbs.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Female natives derive little happiness due to their proud and stubborn nature. Male natives are shrewd and capable. Mula Natives both male and female are good at handling adverse situations and guiding people through difficult times. Through tact and diplomacy Mula natives solve difficult scenarios. Having said that they often quit tasks halfway by influence of Mula ruler Ketu (planet which brings detachment). Mula natives are peace loving with an attractive personality and fixed set of principles. Inspite of numerous adversities they remain optimistic and achieve success in the desired field. On the downside they often overlook adversities and do not plan ahead in life. Due to this peculiar tendency they often invite debt and problems in life. There is no stability in career and there are constant changes of profession. Mula natives are advised to pursue a career where quitting or taking a break is possible. They are good orators and can make a good politician who talks the talk but rarely walks the walk. They can even make a career as financial or religious advisers, fine &nbsp;arts, writers, public speakers, doctors, healers, social work or philosophers.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives generally derive very little benefits through parents. They live a detached life and do not get too close to friends or family. They often have problems with drugs and alcohol addiction. For females marriage may result in unhappiness and even death of husband in some cases. Can have multiple love affairs and troubles through them. for males married life is satisfactory and spouse has all the adequate qualities.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Health: Problems with addictions, dangerous burns, violent accidents and broken bones are all possible.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Good Orators, Spiritual, Adventurous, Brave when Facing Adversities.</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Uncaring, Self-destructive, No Planning.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Mula natives should pray to Ganesha or&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dattatreya" target="_blank">Dattatreya</a></p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:39:19', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:48:17', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:39:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 9, 8, 'mula nakshatra, ganda moola nakshatra, gandmool nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by ketu', 'mula nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 14, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
(53, 184, 'Purva Asadha', 'purva-asadha', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Purva Asadha is the tweentieth nakshatra among the <a title="27 nakshatra category link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=category&amp;id=13&amp;Itemid=120">27 Nakshtaras</a> in Vedic Astrology. The diety for this nakshatra is Apas while the gana is Manushya. The ruling planet for Purva Asadha is <a title="shukra article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=6:shukra&amp;catid=10:9-planets&amp;Itemid=118">Shukra</a> and all the 4 Padas are located in <a title="dhana rashi article link" href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=30:sagittarius&amp;catid=12:12-rashis&amp;Itemid=148">Dhana Rashi</a>. The symbol is a hand fan. Purva Asadha is considered an auspicious nakshatra for female natives but inauspicious for male natives. Honesty is a trait which is best associated with this naksthatra.</p>\r\n<p>Physical Features: Natives have a lean and tall body with beautiful teeth, long ears and arms and narrow waist. Females have a beautiful face, attractive eyes and small lips. They have brown and curly hair and small feet. Female natives are known to put on weight in later years of life.</p>\r\n<p>Character &amp; Events: Purva Asadha natives are known for their honesty. But they have a tendency to jump to conclusions inspite of good intelligence. While they have good argumentative and convincing skills they are too rash in taking actions without proper thought and end up losing. Inspite of loss they are too adamant to accept fault. While they love giving out free advice they resent being advised by others. While outwardly they show to be courageous the inner reality and emotions are quite different. They tend to derive benefits from total strangers. Male natives have low character trait with minimum education and material assets. They may have a harsh and dominating personality but often have to work as underlings. Male natives possess very little administrative skills and can be quite quarrelsome. In a stark contrast female natives have a positive character. They are likely to think over actions before implementing them. They are successful in occupations which allow them to utilize their natural abilities. Period upto 32 years is full of trials. Period between 32 to 50 years suggests progress. As natives have a habit of helping without any expectations of returns career as doctor is highly recommended. Besides that they can work as antique collectors, in fine arts, as poets among other professions.</p>\r\n<p>Family Life: Natives enjoy a healthy relationship with parents and siblings and also derive benefits from them. There are chances to settle abroad if the native desires. Though marriage is delayed, it maybe happy to an extent. Children are talented and respectful. Children also increase the name and fame of the family.</p>\r\n<p>Health: Natives may suffer from an incurable disease. Also there can be breathing troubles, bronchitis, etc. Thigh problems and lung disorders like rheumatism possible.</p>\r\n<p>Positives: Artistic, Good looking, Influential</p>\r\n<p>Negatives: Stubborn, Inflexible, Egoistic.</p>\r\n<p>Remedies: Prayers to a calm goddess deity like Laxmi, Parvati, Saraswati or Mother Mary.&nbsp;</p>', '', 1, 13, '2014-02-02 02:40:04', 899, '', '2014-04-21 09:50:44', 899, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-02-02 02:40:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":""}', 13, 7, 'purva asadha nakshatra, nakshatra ruled by shukra', 'purva asadha nakshatra in vedic astrology', 1, 19, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', '');
